        "zh": "1. 資料蒐集與整理<br>2. 資料敘述與表現<br>3. 機率<br>4. 間斷性隨機變數<br>5. 連續性隨機變數<br>",
        "en": "1. Collection and presentation of data<br>2. Description and summary of data<br>3. Probability<br>4. Discrete random variable<br>5. Continuous random variable"
